{"tid":1582880,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"用咗幾日時間終於搞完部新腦，折騰咗真係耐到燥底","createTime":"2019-09-20T10:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T03:16:39.000Z","uid":318461,"like":0,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"20f651de1d12ad4b8650bc6e4f27c97f39f23465","tid":1582880,"uid":318461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"哎，念住玩RGB順便換埋d 新CPU，原本念住今個月換咗個board同CPU先，淘寶淘翻來送買240水冷，之後發現舊機箱擺唔到，前日又買個機箱，之後比埋個sales hard sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，買埋條ram同火牛，不知不覺除左顯卡都換咗新。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身其實冇咩野，當普通砌機咁砌，但因爲第一次用水冷搞到頭大，冷頭有兩條綫無知邊個打邊個，RGB我知插邊，但其他綫5g插邊啦，之後就on99以爲Pump fan係水冷風扇插咗，水泵就插咗CPU FAN，之後開機發現CPU benchmark同溫度都5對路，以爲自己中彩就去問賣家啦，後來又調轉插又係一樣，之後費事煩就換返AMD原裝RGB風扇。溫度瞬間正常好多，5g係咪個水冷坏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!?<br />\n<br />\n其實砌完機后發現運行得好慢，當初就係以爲CPU有事，點知換埋風扇,CPU溫度同benchmark正常都係lag，格式化咗ssd重裝又係lag，之後就換咗個SATA綫同PORT位到SATA 1,2，即刻順暢返，就係想問係咪主板識別係由第一開始先會運行得快/PORT位有問題/綫出咗問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家搞點好部腦，念下原裝RGB風扇都几正就用住先，水冷就擺咗一邊冇理，得閑再裝上去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順便想吐槽下CORSAIR質地都5多掂ze，買ge機箱係SPEC OMEGA RGB，第一次開個前蓋就爆咗兩個阻塞片。另外個側面玻璃上有d橡膠米防止你扭螺絲整親個玻璃ge，點知5係固定ge，搞到我跌咗個5g去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，真係買個千銀機箱比人感覺咁差，以後5敢再買corsair d 野。"},{"pid":"c24ce462afc792b48fc6d60ea935c6725b9b5548","tid":1582880,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8nHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=9ceff562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"94c81928aeda76c4956f5601165dfb4c2d08fe60","tid":1582880,"uid":196924,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"念你老母<br />\n淘你老豆寶<br />\n5你全家<br />\n顯你祖宗十八代卡<br />\n仲有冇，淨係睇到咁多"},{"pid":"779ddede7ab177a92160d8b42ff4eafe8db7b74e","tid":1582880,"uid":13494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"94c81928aeda76c4956f5601165dfb4c2d08fe60","tid":1582880,"uid":196924,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"念你老母<br />\n淘你老豆寶<br />\n5你全家<br />\n顯你祖宗十八代卡<br />\n仲有冇，淨係睇到咁多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"坏 綫 几<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf47958c4791262cb90b6ab2bbb3d82cd5898e3","tid":1582880,"uid":308567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20